short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: A new tab page focused on all the information you need right now.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Telescope reimagines your new tab page by bringing the data you need from services you use directly to you. Get going quickly by adding bookmarks to get to your next website, check off that todo item, or just browse the web quickly.

Telescope's integrations include: 
- Bringing autocomplete and search with Google, Bing, DuckDuckGo or Ecosia
- Integration with your Todoist tasks to bring them front and center.
- Integration with the Australian BOM to provide weather information on your homepage.
